title: THURSDAY - Week 15 QB injury news 2020
itunes:title: THURSDAY - Week 15 QB injury news 2020
description:
In what could be a Super Bowl preview, the Chiefs and Saints will battle it out on Sunday (0:07), but will New Orleans have Drew Brees (0:45) back under center? We also have the latest on Alex Smith's (1:13) leg injury. A pair of former Oklahoma QBs prepare for a Sooner showdown (1:41), plus the Buccaneers will be without their top running back (2:39). And Thursday Night Football kicks off with an AFC West showdown (4:05) when the Chargers take on the Raiders
